title: USACO Guide
description: USACO Guide is a follow along guide to competitive programming. Each section is focused around a different competitive programming concept. The section includes an article with detailed information on the algorithms and ideas needed. The end of each section also includes a list of problems that utilize the current topic. If you feel like you don't know where to start in competitive programming, it allows you to follow a structured approach.
